==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Etna
<hw>Et"na</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A kind of small,
portable, cooking apparatus for which heat is furnished by a spirit
lamp.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>There should certainly be an <qex>etna</qex> for getting a hot cup
of coffee in a hurry.</q> <rj><qau>V. Baker.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Etnean</ent>⟦br⟧
